      },
      {
        title: 'Do you offer training for our team?',
        description:
          'Yes. We don’t just hand over a shiny solution and walk away. We train end‑users, admins and your nominated SharePoint Champions so your team feels confident, capable and not secretly Googling “how do I use this?” after go‑live.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How long does a typical SharePoint project take?',
        description:
          'It depends on the size of the project. Smaller builds can be wrapped up in weeks, while bigger, more complex ones may take a few months. After the discovery session, you’ll get a clearer timeline you can trust.',
